# tests/

Comprehensive BATS-based test suite for Intent v2.5.0 with 15+ tests validating CLI commands, workflows, and core functionality. Tests are organized into unit tests (by command category), integration tests (full workflows), and shared test utilities. Ensures Intent CLI works correctly across its feature set.

## Dirs

- `fixtures/` -- Test fixtures and sample files for tests
- `integration/` -- Integration tests validating complete user workflows and end-to-end scenarios
- `lib/` -- Shared BATS test libraries, helpers, and assertion utilities
- `unit/` -- Unit tests organized by command category (14 test files for individual commands)

## Files

- `run_tests.sh` -- Test runner script with Bats orchestration, color output, and configuration
- `core_functionality.bats` -- Essential smoke tests validating Intent infrastructure and core functionality
- `README.md` -- Test documentation, prerequisites, running instructions, and structure guide
